reviews.text: Good quality and good price. Just a bit too crowded.

We were seated by the entrance near the stairs which can easily smell the burning incense sticks outside the restaurant, which was quite unpleasant to dine with. Overall the food are not that authentic and the marinated goose slices tasted a bit too gamey.

Very nice Chiu Chow Authentic cuisine with great quality ingredients is the key of great restaurant. Goose slices, Oyster omelette, crispy chicken, mixed prawn and cashew nuts stirred fire vegetables are some of the great food you must try.

Very good food. Need to make reservations ahead.
Enjoy the dining experience.
Very nice Chinese food !

reviews.text: Good quality and good price. Just a bit too crowded.
夫家係潮州人都喜歡呢度，地方細細勝在乾乾淨淨，茶棵，芋泥唔係度度有得食，一定會再去
食物水準不過不失，一般潮州菜味道，冇太大驚喜。炒飯夠干身，價格合理。因枱與枱比較貼及樓底低，所以比較嘈吵。如果多人，建議訂房，會較舒適，但有最低消費。
價錢合理味道好，香港很難找到像樣的潮州美食👍🏻
凍蟹超好食，傳統的粿做得好好，胡椒豬肚湯夠味夠啦，超正！！！價錢非常合理！！
